{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji48.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于北大“六·一八”事件","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于北大“六·一八”事件川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1966年7月）“六·一八”事件不是反革命事件，而是革命事件。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1966年6月18日，北京大学发生了全校性的大规模暴力斗争，60多名教员和干部遭到游街、戴高帽子、罚跪和殴打等。后来，北大工作组制止了这些斗争。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":430,"page_end":430},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}